  "description": "Defines a contract for objects that can be serialized to JSON format.",
  "title": "Interface IJsonSerializable",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_IJsonSerializable'>Interface IJsonSerializable    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/IJsonSerializable.cs#L47'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Defines a contract for objects that can be serialized to JSON format.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public interface IJsonSerializable</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Remarks</h2><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Types implementing this interface can provide their own serialization logic by defining\nwhich properties should be included and how their values should be represented.\nUsage Pattern:\nClasses should implement this interface to support JSON serialization through the\nJsonNativeAot.Serialize&lt;T&gt; method.\nNote: For complete bidirectional serialization support, also implement\nIJsonDesSerializable&lt;T&gt; to enable deserialization.</p>\n<h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.GetSerializableProperties' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.GetSerializableProperties' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Data_Json_IJsonSerializable_GetSerializableProperties'>GetSerializableProperties()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Data/src/Json/IJsonSerializable.cs#L80'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the serializable properties of this instance.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>[ExcludeFromCodeCoverage]\nIEnumerable&lt;(string PropertyName, string Value)&gt; GetSerializableProperties()</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.ienumerable-1'>IEnumerable</a>&lt;(<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.valuetuple-system.string,system.string-.propertyname'>PropertyName</a>, <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.valuetuple-system.string,system.string-.value'>Value</a>)&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">An enumerable of tuples containing property names and their string representations.\nProperty names should not include quotes; values may be primitives or raw JSON.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Remarks</h4><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Implementation Guide:</p>\n<ul sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"2\">\n<li sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"2\">Use yield return for each property: (propertyName, stringValue)</li>\n<li sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"3\">Primitive values should be converted to strings (e.g., number.ToString())</li>\n<li sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"4\">Complex values (objects/arrays) should return raw JSON strings</li>\n<li sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Data.Json.IJsonSerializable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"5\">Null or empty values are allowed and will be handled by the serializer\nTime Complexity: Should be O(n) where n is the number of properties.\nExample:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-csharp\">public class Person : IJsonSerializable\n{\n    public string Name { get; set; }\n    public int Age { get; set; }\n    public List&lt;string&gt; Tags { get; set; }\n\n    public IEnumerable&lt;(string PropertyName, string Value)&gt; GetSerializableProperties()\n    {\n        yield return (\"Name\", Name);\n        yield return (\"Age\", Age.ToString());\n        yield return (\"Tags\", \"[\\\"tag1\\\",\\\"tag2\\\"]\");\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n",
  "yamlmime": "ApiPage",
